### Get All Art (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/art

### Get Art with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/art?page=1&limit=10

### Get Art by ID
# Replace with actual UUID after creating art
GET {{baseUrl}}/art/{{artId}}

### Search Art by query
GET {{baseUrl}}/art/search?q=battle

### Search Art by book
GET {{baseUrl}}/art/search?bookId={{bookId}}

### Search Art by chapter
GET {{baseUrl}}/art/search?chapterId={{chapterId}}

### Search Art with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/art/search?q=storm&bookId={{bookId}}

### Create Art (basic - book only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/art
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookId": "{{bookId}}",
  "title": "The Bridge Four Salute",
  "description": "Bridge Four giving their iconic salute.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/bridge-four-salute.jpg",
  "tags": ["bridge four", "kaladin", "soldiers"]
}

### Create Art (with chapter)
POST {{baseUrl}}/art
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{bookId}}",
  "chapterId": "{{chapterId}}",
  "title": "Szeth in the Night",
  "description": "Szeth-son-son-Vallano performing his deadly mission.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/szeth-assassination.jpg",
  "artistId": "{{artistId}}",
  "tags": ["szeth", "assassination", "prologue"]
}

### Create Art with Character/Location/Item associations
POST {{baseUrl}}/art
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{bookId}}",
  "chapterId": "{{chapterId}}",
  "title": "Kaladin on the Shattered Plains",
  "description": "Kaladin wielding his spear during a bridge run.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/kaladin-bridge-run.jpg",
  "artistId": "{{artistId}}",
  "tags": ["kaladin", "bridge run", "action"],
  "characters": ["{{characterId}}"],
  "locations": ["{{locationId}}"],
  "items": ["{{itemId}}"]
}

